{"/service/ndnp/iahi/batch_iahi_jackson_ver01/data/sn86061215/00415668764/1908010901/0637.xml":{"full_text":"4T.\n\u2022A.* i.\n\u00abJ\n4*\n4\u00bb\n4*\n4*\n4*\n\u2022v\n4\u00bb\n4\n4*\n4\n4\u00bb\n4*\n4*\n4*\n4\nj-\n4\n8., ^THURSDAY, January 9, 1908.\nYOUR\nOffice open daily from 9:00 a. m.\nuntil 8:00 p, tti.\nietfj-'\u2022:\"\nUntil Saturday Night 9:00\np.<p></p>DPS\nFirst National Bank Building,\nDrs, Keith Co. have been located in Ottumwa for a long time a.nd have\ncured patients all over this section of the country, who will testify as to their\nskill, and if you are skeptical or doubt their ability you can ask any of your\nneighbors who have taken their treatment and they will tell you the results ob\"\ntained from Drs. Keith Co's. treatment and in most of cases were cured after\nthey had been unsuccessfully treated by one or many other physicians.\nIf you are sick or afflicted in any way a:nd wish the best treatment, plai to\nconsult these doctors at once.\nBe examined and find out your true condition.\nIt will cost you nothing for consultation or examination and whether you are\ntreated or not, you will be welcome,\nDrs. Keith Co. treat CHRONIC, SPECIAL AND PRIVATE DISEASES\nOF MEN, WOMEN AND CHILDREN.\nThey have every appliance needed to give you scientific high grade attention.\nDon't put off till tomorrow what you should do today.\nI0\n-4\nBut every day your disease is progressing slow and sure.\nif\u00bb^\nS\nTHE OTTUM^TA. COURIER\nTHIS IS\nDon't Fail to Take Advantage of This Special Offer\nWill be Treated Until Cured for\nOne-Half Regular Price\nThis offer is made solely to benefit the great numbers of afflicted people who are in need of Spe\ncialty Treatment, but who feel they are unable to avail themselves of Specialty Skill on account of\nscarcity of money.\nThe financial panic is over, prices and business are sure to return to their former standard and in\na short time money will be as plentiful as ever.\nThe Special One-Half Price will more than make up for the scarcity of money and Drs. Keith\nCo. will give you their very best skill and attention, the same as if you were paying the regular price.\nDrs. Keith fif Co. are permanent fixtures in Ottumwa and feel positive that everyone who ac\ncepts this offer will recommend their friends for treatment after they are cured.\nDRS. KEITH CO.\n115 South Market Street\nConsultation and Examination FREE.\nSpecial Notice to Out of\nTown People\nAll people living out cf the city that commence treatment before January, 12th, will not only be given\nthe treatment at one-half the regular price, but DR. KEITH will pay their raiload and other expenses neces\nsary to make the trip to OTTUiMWA and return.\nAny one unable to call is invited to write regarding their cases and opinion will be furnished free of charge.\n\\St\nm. January 11th, All Curable Cases That Start Treatment With\n*?$fe*aw\u00abL\n7\nf%\nt'k\n\u2014r-\nCO.,\nDon't allow these little aches and pains that you have been having to go\nwithout attention. Don't think that you can wear out your disease, for it surely\nwill wear you out first.\nDon't think next month will do as well as now for many cases that can be\ncured now will become incurable in a short time.\nYou know that something is wrong and have beeti warned that you\nare not in perfect health, so do not allow these warnings to go unheeded.\nIt is a sacred duty that you owe to yourself and family to get well and\nenjoy life and be able to cope with your neighbors in every way.\nDon't think because you have tried and been unsuccessful in treatment that\nyou cannot be cured for it is possible that your case is still curable, and after ex\namination you will be told frankly whether you can be cured or not.\nWhat ever may be YOUR TROUBLE call and find out regarding your case.\nREMEMBER THE NAME\n4\n\u00ab-JV 4%-U rlK a.wf\nz*\u2122\nOTTUMWA, IOWA\nFirst National Bank Building\nOTTUMWA, IOWA\nS\nim\n4\n4\n4\nW9&\nHi:\nSpi\nll\n\"Ti if\"\n4\nIT \"vr\n3L\n4\